title: Collection of custom trance edits
description:
A collection of trance tracks for people like me that prefer their trance in a short and "radio-friendly" length. This includes 28 tracks that has never been available, or atleast at the time of editing not easily available, in short format. This is not a hodgepodge job, genuine time and effort has gone into putting them together.

The tracks included are:
4 Strings - Diving (Anders Hammar's Minimalistix Radio Edit)
Alex Bartlett - My Angel (Anders Hammar's 2Players Radio Edit)
Andy B - Imagination (Anders Hammar's MP Radio Edit)
Art Of Trance feat Michele Adamsson - Love Washes Over (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Caater - Master Tune (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Caracas - Through The Barricades (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Darren Tate vs Jono Grant - Let The Light Shine In (Anders Hammar's Vocal Radio Edit)
DT8 Project feat Andrea Britton - Winter (Anders Hammar's GD Edit)
DT8 Project feat Andrea Britton - Winter (Anders Hammar's Ian Knowles Edit)
Eon - Pocket Damage (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Fire & Ice feat Edvika - Close To Me (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Hi-Gate - Hurricane (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Ian Van Dahl - Try (Anders Hammar's Michael Woods Radio Edit)
Jan Johnston - Am I On Pause (Anders Hammar's Trailer Trash Radio Edit)
Jan Johnston - Calling Your Name (Anders Hammar's Thrillseekers Radio Edit)
Laguna - Unforgiven (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Lange feat Leah - Don't Think It (Feel It) (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Matt Darey & Marcella Woods - U Shine On (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
OceanLab - Beautiful Together (Anders Hammar's Signum Radio Edit)
OceanLab - Sky Falls Down (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Ralph Fridge - Angel (Anders Hammar's Short Edit)
Scooter - Devil Drums (Anders Hammar's Short Edit)
System F - Needle Juice (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Tenth Planet - Walk On Water (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
Terraformer - Won't Forget These Days (Anders Hammar's Radio Edit)
The Quest - C Sharp (Anders Hammar's Short Edit)
Ulrich Fassbinder - 20000 Miles (Anders Hammar's Silverblue Radio Edit)
Veracocha vs Axwell - Feel the Carte Blanche (Anders Hammar's Short Edit)

I hope you like them.
